	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Today I learned that Sinking Feeling is a CNROM with two CHR ROM banks, but $0A00-$0FFF and $1200-$1FFF of bank 0 are empty, as is $1000-$1FFF of bank 1. This means moving the sprite tiles from $1000-$11FF to $0E00-$0FFF and then moving the used half to $1000-$1FFF of bank 0 would convert it to NROM.<br /><br />calima: Could you do this for me? It'd simplify the multicart construction.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


